==English==
===Proper noun===
'''[[Georgian]] [[Soviet Socialist Republic|SSR]]'''
# Georgian Soviet Socialist Republic, the name for the [[Georgia|Republic of Georgia]] while under the rule of the [[Soviet Union]] (1936-1991, named changed in 1990).

